@startuml
title Publish Ad

actor "Advertiser" as Advertiser
participant "__:System__" as System
actor "Media Owner" as MediaOwner

' 1. The Advertiser browses available media listings and selects one.
Advertiser -> System: getMedia()
' 1.1 System retrieves details for the selected media listing and displays the details page.
System --> Advertiser: displayMediaDetails()

' 2. The Advertiser clicks on the “Reserve” button.
Advertiser -> System: reserveMedia()
' 2.1 System displays a reservation modal.
System --> Advertiser: showReservationModal()

' 3. The Advertiser selects an ad (or adds a new one), selects dates and presses next.
Advertiser -> System: submitAd(mediaId, adImage, startDate, endDate)
' 3.1 System shows a preview of the ad on the selected media.
System --> Advertiser: showAdPreviewOnMedia()

' 4. User presses the next button.
Advertiser -> System: goToPayment()
' 4.1 System shows the payment screen.
System --> Advertiser: showPaymentScreen()

' 5. User enters credit card info and clicks reserve.
Advertiser -> System: confirmReservation(paymentDetails)
' 5.1 System closes the modal in the frontend.
System --> Advertiser: closeModalAndShowConfirmation()
' 5.2 System backend processes the request and emails Media Owner.
System -> MediaOwner: sendAdRequestEmail(adDetails)

@enduml
